/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭單一問<br />\n平時for輸血既血點嚟？<br />\n斷估都應該冇乜主人會肯俾寵物捐血"},{"pid":"f3c113732973a329d9b6802566900abf2ef56d97","tid":2137304,"uid":107740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T01:34:49.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"da1da0c99a08076a73e6979ef04840ae81197c84","tid":2137304,"uid":215035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T01:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"},{"pid":"2e5fa0442d19e492e2ee69ca74a300259ec55ac0","tid":2137304,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T01:39:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d3b911927579f28ce97b00d63af269308010a8","tid":2137304,"uid":224270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eea23f2a416bd76623075733fc82023fc5ebcba","tid":2137304,"uid":297670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f565859a370561e580df1f1fdf462e246bd1b606","tid":2137304,"uid":364771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T00:45:17.000Z","msg":"狗狗係咩事要捐血?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T00:49:12.000Z","msg":"個肚附近有個腫瘤，仲爆埋所以要做手術。琴日做咗一次之後情況都穩定。但仲要做埋第二次手術，不過佢本身血小板唔夠，所以要其他狗狗幫下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:41:02.000Z","msg":"良性定惡性？"},{"pid":"6bc165b2df49537d7e828499f0b7372e631053fd","tid":2137304,"uid":55657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:43:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a05d682794c498419b4352aff7076df24d6fc1f9","tid":2137304,"uid":152090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:48:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce23586abd46f0cd1d15058825981b1b25fab940","tid":2137304,"uid":297670,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:01:11.000Z","msg":"[ Update ]<br />\n<br />\n啱啱見